<tbody>
<row><entry align=center>Type</entry><entry align=center>Symbol</entry><entry align=center>Description</entry></row>
<row><entry>Right Tab Stop</entry><entry><graphic fileref="rtab" format="png" align="center"></graphic></entry>
<entry spanname=hspan>With a right tab stop, the right edge of the next set of words is aligned at the tab stop. </entry></row>
<row><entry></entry></row>
<row><entry></entry><entry></entry><entry align=right><emphasis>Example:</emphasis></entry><entry align=left><graphic fileref="rtab2" format="png" align="center"></graphic></entry></row>
<row><entry></entry></row>
<row><entry>Center Tab Stop</entry><entry><graphic fileref="ctab" format="png" align="center"></graphic></entry>
<entry spanname=hspan>With a right tab stop, the text is centered at the tab stop. </entry></row>
<row><entry></entry></row>
