<row><entry>Left Tab Stop</entry><entry><graphic fileref="ltab" format="png" align="center"></graphic></entry>
<entry spanname=hspan>With a left tab stop, the left edge of the next set of words is aligned at the tab stop. </entry></row>
<row><entry></entry></row>
<row><entry></entry><entry></entry><entry align=right><emphasis>Example:</emphasis></entry><entry align=left><graphic fileref="ltab2" format="png" align="center"></graphic></entry></row>
